ed imaging\nis far from being fully exploited, and further progress will lead to\nsignificant improvements of clinical X-ray CT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Jan 2023 18:10:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-03"}
