ies of corresponding hybrid jets in order to interpret polarization\nmeasurements of the prompt emission in our sample.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Jan 2023 09:35:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-03"}
